“'''Every time you masturbate...  God kills a kitten'''”是一张2002年出现在{{link-en|Fark.com|Fark}}的图片，经[[互联网|互联网]]传播成为[[网络迷因|网络迷因]]<ref name="fark">{{cite web|url=http://www.fark.com/farq/farkisms/|title=Fark Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ): Farkisms|publisher=Fark|access-date=2016-12-27|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605085325/https://www.fark.com/farq/farkisms/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Horen|first=Tom|url=http://www.startribune.com/lifestyle/style/31178504.html|title=Domo: From underground to advertiser|newspaper=Star Tribune|date=2008-10-20|access-date=2016-12-17|archive-date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903161750/http://www.startribune.com/lifestyle/style/31178504.html}}</ref>。图片内容为一只猫被两只[[Domo君|Domo君]]追逐，下有副标题为Please, think of the kittens（请为猫着想）。

== 起源 ==
1996年，[[乔治城大学|乔治城大学]]旗下讽刺杂志《The Gonzo》出版了一副猫的图片，下边附有文字：“事实：每当你[[手淫|手淫]]，[[神_(一神教)|上帝]]都会杀死一只小猫。还要死多少猫？”（Fact: Every Time You Masturbate, God Kills a Kitten. How Many More Have to Die?）<ref>{{cite web | title = The Gonzo #10 | url = http://www.shlomiraz.com/Site/The_Gonzo/Pages/Issue_10.html#0}}{{dead link|date=2009-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Stryker|first=Cole|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=y3QjCQAAQBAJ&pg=PT69&dq=everytime+you+masturbate+god+kills+a+kitten#v=onepage&q=kitten|title=Epic Win for Anonymous: How 4chan's Army Conquered the Web|publisher=Peter Mayer Publishers|date=2011|access-date=2016-12-27|isbn=9781590207383}}</ref>。

